🚀 Task 1: Content Generation with Prompt Engineering

🔹 Objective: Use prompt chains to generate engaging YouTube video titles, long-form scripts, and thumbnail ideas in a selected niche. Then, transform these outputs into a complete YouTube video using AI tools.

🛠️ Tools & Platforms

ChatGPT → Script & title generation

Pictory / InVideo → Script-to-video conversion

Canva → Thumbnail design / video slides

DALL·E / Midjourney → AI-generated thumbnail images

Notion → Documentation & workflow tracking

📦 Deliverables

✅ Prompt chain documentation (clear step-by-step prompts)

✅ YouTube video script (800–1500 words, engaging & structured)

✅ Thumbnail text + AI-generated image or mockup

✅ Final video (edited and AI-powered)

🎯 Skills Demonstrated

Prompt chaining for structured AI outputs

Long-form AI content generation

Thumbnail concept writing for AI image tools

Storyboarding and video creation with AI editors

Packaging content for YouTube growth & marketing

